Blockchain meets Luxury Hospitality

Eden Luxury Token (ELUX) is a BEP-20 utility token designed to revolutionize the high-end hospitality and sustainable tourism sector through blockchain innovation.

The ELUX initiative aims to build a premium hospitality ecosystem starting from Dubai (UAE), integrating Web3 technologies, VIP luxury services, and asset-backed development opportunities.

